#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "http / https"
msgstr "http / https"

#. Tag: author
#: index.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Lauri.Watts; &Lauri.Watts.mail;"
msgstr "&लौरी.वाट्स; &लौरी.वाट्स.मेल;"

#. Tag: trans_comment
#: index.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "ROLES_OF_TRANSLATORS"
msgstr "अनुवादकानां_भूमिका"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&HTTP; is the <emphasis>H</emphasis>yper<emphasis>T</emphasis>ext "
"<emphasis>T</emphasis>ransfer <emphasis>P</emphasis>rotocol."
msgstr ""
"&HTTP; इति <emphasis>H</emphasis>yper<emphasis>T</emphasis>ext <emphasis>T</"
"emphasis>ransfer <emphasis>P</emphasis>rotocol इति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The http KIO worker is used by all &kde; applications to handle connections "
"to &HTTP; servers, that is, web servers. The most common usage is to view "
"web pages in the &konqueror; web browser."
msgstr ""
"http KIO कार्यकर्ता सर्वैः &kde; &HTTP; सर्वरः अर्थात् जालसर्वरः । सर्वाधिकं सामान्यं "
"उपयोगः &konqueror; जालपुटम्।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the https KIO worker in &konqueror; by giving it a &URL;. "
"<userinput>https://<replaceable>www.kde.org</replaceable></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"भवान् &konqueror; तस्मै &URL;. <userinput>https://<प्रतिस्थापनीय>www.kde.org</"
"replaceable></userinput> ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "https is http encapsulated in a SSL/TLS stream."
msgstr "https इति http SSL/TLS धारायां समाहितम् अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"SSL is the Secure Sockets Layer protocol, a security protocol that provides "
"communications privacy over the Internet. The protocol allows client/server "
"applications to communicate in a way that is designed to prevent "
"eavesdropping, tampering, or message forgery."
msgstr ""
"SSL इति Secure Sockets Layer प्रोटोकॉल इति सुरक्षाप्रोटोकॉलः यः अन्तर्जालमाध्यमेन "
"संचारगोपनीयतां प्रदाति । प्रोटोकॉल क्लायन्ट्/सर्वर-अनुप्रयोगानाम् संवादं कर्तुं शक्नोति यत् "
"श्रवणं, छेड़छाड़ं, सन्देशजालीकरणं वा निवारयितुं विनिर्मितम् अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "TLS stands for Transport Layer Security."
msgstr "TLS इत्यस्य अर्थः Transport Layer Security इति ।"
